{"tid":2288213,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來好多人唔知電腦系統都有得用深夜模式，決定行善教吓大家","createTime":"2020-11-16T10:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T11:09:07.000Z","uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2f3f1611bb857bd20483dd68c8a5497530541874","tid":2288213,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:37:07.000Z","msg":"事先聲明，此文由本人宇城飛一字一句打出來<br />\n嚴禁在未得到本人同意下轉載本文<br />\n否則本人會採取相應法律行動<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">如不同意以上聲明，請立即離開本POST</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1)作業系統設定深夜模式，如果係用WIN10，<br />\n&quot;開始&quot;&gt;&quot;設定&quot;&gt;&quot;個人化&quot;&gt;&quot;色彩&quot;&gt;&quot;選擇顏色&quot;&gt;&quot;深色&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bEMyBRU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbEMyBRU.png&h=15bc4c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2)瀏覽器設定深夜模式，如果係用Chrome，打開Chrome，<br />\n在網址欄輸入&quot;chrome://flags/#enable-force-dark&quot;，<br />\n然後會見到有項&quot;Force Dark Mode for Web Contents&quot; &gt;<br />\n右手邊有選項將&quot;Default&quot;改為&quot;Enabled&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8dhFgSa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8dhFgSa.png&h=0ae05d49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">YOU ARE WELCOME</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b150092eb937a92bdc9381f6d85edfe60354f261","tid":2288213,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"嘔完血？"},{"pid":"88da11f704a5daac30495d99dc56d8ebaf0b6ef8","tid":2288213,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b150092eb937a92bdc9381f6d85edfe60354f261","tid":2288213,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"嘔完血？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T10:39:48.000Z","msg":"飲完菊花荼好似無咩事"},{"pid":"981ab8b15e5c4f65b8ba4d1fa222dcd19aab7cea","tid":2288213,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor